About me

I am a post-graduate student pursuing a Master of IT in Business (Analytics) at Singapore Management University. Before venturing into the world of analytics, I spent 6 years in the auditing and financial due diligence department at PwC Singapore.

About this blog

This blog is dedicated to showcase my assignments and project work relating to the Visual Analytics and Applications course (ISSS608) at Singapore Management University.
